  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Measurement of bone length in subjects diagnosed with kyphosis and scoliosis using the Lunar
      iDXA x-ray scan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine if bone density scanning (DEXA) and the use of a computer software program can
      make accurate measurements of the curvature(s) of the spine (Cobb angle)in patients with
      kyphosis and scoliosis compared to x-rays of the spine.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
